# Highlight Selection – BMAD (Agent-Driven AI Workflow)

This project implements the same highlight selection engine using a BMAD agent-driven AI workflow.

The implementation was produced through an AI-assisted iterative development process.

This repository is part of a Generative AI Evangelist technical assignment.

## Overview

Input:
- match events (goal, assist, card)
- user preference (favorite player, favorite team)

Output:
- ranked highlights
- score for each event
- explanation of the ranking

## Scoring Model

Base event scores

- goal = 4
- assist = 3
- card = 1

Preference boosts

- favorite player +8
- favorite team +5

## Run

python src/highlight_selector.py

